                    Don't say fuck it to everything in life, just to the unimportant things<br><br>
                    Whether you realize it or not, you are always choosing what to give a fuck about.<br>
                    The key is to gradually prune the things you care about, <br>
                    so that you only give a fuck on the most important of occasions. -->
                </p>
                    <div>
                        <a href="/books" class="btn btn-primary create-account">Back</a>
                    </div>
            </div>
